<lb ed="B" n="0159b11"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="8"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0159b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">佛國寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>佛國寺<note place="inline">古剎　勅賜</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0159b13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1301" style="margin-left:1em">在都城外東城地南去太平門二里東南去所綂靈谷
<lb ed="B" n="0159b14"/>寺十八里蔣山西畔古華藏菴景泰間僧妙慶募建奏
<lb ed="B" n="0159b15"/>賜今額所領小剎曰普濟菴清果寺梵惠院茶亭菴地
<lb ed="B" n="0159b16"/>藏菴</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0159b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1703" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">鐘樓</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1707" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">鐘樓<note place="inline">壹座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">天王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1711" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">天王殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左伽藍殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1716" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左伽藍殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右祖師殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1722" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右祖師殿
<lb ed="B" n="0159b18"/><note place="inline">叄楹</note>正佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1808" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">肆房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址叄拾伍畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b1812" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址叄拾伍畆<note place="inline">東至本寺官墳　南至刑部墻
<lb ed="B" n="0159b19"/>　西至官路　北至官路</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0159b20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">田山</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159b2003" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">田山<note place="inline">共貳拾貳畆叄分</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0160a" n="0160a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">藏經護勅</cb:mulu><head>藏經護勅<note place="inline">文同靈谷</note></head></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">文</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">【文】</note></head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛國寺記略</cb:mulu><head>佛國寺記略</head><byline cb:type="author">明禮部尚書毘陵胡濙</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a03"/><p xml:id="pB29p0160a0301">寺在京都太平門外二里許相傳古華藏菴也無碑可考
<lb ed="B" n="0160a04"/>不知創始何時荒廢<note n="0160a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0160a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>久基址猶存形勢雄偉最為勝處
<lb ed="B" n="0160a05"/>僧妙慶化募眾緣鳩工集材誅茅剪<g ref="#CB00331"/>凡殿堂廊廡以次
<lb ed="B" n="0160a06"/>建立鍾魚振揚香積芬苾繚以穹垣種植松栢於景泰五
<lb ed="B" n="0160a07"/>年六月十有八日奏　請賜額為佛國寺　欽賜藏經
<lb ed="B" n="0160a08"/>　勅諭<g ref="#CB31131"/>為護持　天順元年八月</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">詩</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">【詩】</note></head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">遊佛國寺</cb:mulu><head>遊佛國寺</head><byline cb:type="author">明王韋</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a10"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0160a1001" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>嶂開佳麗地門對泬寥天幽室憐容膝塵勞喜息肩望窮
<lb ed="B" n="0160a11"/>鴻鳫外歌向菊花前回首重城路鐘聲隔暮煙</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">普濟菴</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>普濟菴</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0160a13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0160a1301" style="margin-left:1em">在都城太平門外半里東城牧馬所地西北去所領佛
<lb ed="B" n="0160a14"/>國寺二里與城隣近</p>
